<br>
But here is my take.<br>
<br>
Ragefire spawned - they failed - they lose their chance.<br>
<br>
If they can prove there was deliberate and malicious training involved then they should have gotten the GM's involved. Since this didn't happen we really have no way of verifying it wasn't someone from their own guild that accidentaly trained them trying to make it to help kill the dragon (This is unfortunate but it happens to all of us at some time)<br>
<br>
